sourcesContent: import { useContext } from "react" import { GlobalContext } from "../../contexts/global/GlobalContext" import { ContainerTableData } from "./styled" const TableData = () => { const { states } = useContext(GlobalContext) return First Name Last Name Participation { states.users.map((user, index) => { return {index + 1} {user.firstName} {user.lastName} {user.participation}% }) } } export default TableData
